                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/2819" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-0421</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10572 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机不可失，时不再来:技术服务公司创业之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Opportunity Knocks But Once:  a Technical Service Company’s Road to Entrepreneurship</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陈婧，周宁，韩世海，蒙姝，韩小汀，李晓晶，孙文彬</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京航空航天大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">诺海通公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通讯业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">质量管理部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">49 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">技术服务公司；创业机会发现；创业机会评价；创业机会把握；2017百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">technical service company, entrepreneurial opportunity discovery, entrepreneurial opportunity evaluation, entrepreneurial opportunity exploitation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着国内外通信技术的不断革新，网络制式已从最初满足通话的2G时代，发展到以数据话务为主的3G时代，再到以大数据流量4G、5G的革命。在通信技术服务领域迅猛发展的大背景下，越来越多的创业者瞄准通信技术服务领域，以其为主营业务的创业公司大量涌现。本文以赵福洪创办诺海通公司过程中对创业机会的三次发现、评价、把握为案例研究对象，通过描述主人公从一位文科毕业生到技术专家，再到自己创业的十年经历，探究了创业者在创业过程中应如何不断地识别机会、评价机会与把握机会，并进一步分析创业过程创业者应具备的素质及应遵循的决策逻辑。由此，本案例希望能为创业者如何快速实现成功提供借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the continuous advancements of communication technologies, the standard of mobile telecommunication technologies has evolved from the 2G, which fulfills the basic needs for telecommunication, to the 3G with data traffic provided, and further towards 4G and 5G with broadband data traffic provided. The rapid development of communication technology services has been attracting a growing number of entrepreneurs’ attention. Start-up companies specialized in communications technology services therefore emerge in large numbers. This case described the discovery, evaluation and exploitation of entrepreneurial opportunities along the developmental journey of Beijing Nuohaitong Company founded by Mr. Fuhong Zhao. In ten years’ time, Mr. Zhao turned himself from a fresh graduate of Arts to a technical expert and eventually became an entrepreneur in his industry.  The experience of Mr. Zhao dealing with his three major entrepreneurial opportunities sheds lights on how to discover, evaluate and exploit opportunities, as well as the key behavioral traits and decision-making logics of a successful entrepreneur. This case therefore has practical implications for potential entrepreneurs.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2017</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创业管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">创业企业、创业机会、创业者的素质以及创业企业如何可持续发展</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2017-08</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
